### **Mostrar los vuelos junto con la capacidad de su aeronave asignada**
```sql
SELECT f.id,
       f.pax_count,
       (SELECT capacity FROM Aircraft a WHERE a.id = f.aircraft) AS aircraft_capacity
FROM Flight f;
```
